| **Canopy** | Half-sphere dome (red) with a darker underside |
| **Ribs** | 8 gold rods radiating across the canopy surface |
| **Top tip** | Small gold cone at the apex |
| **Shaft** | Dark metallic cylinder extending downward |
| **Handle** | Curved J-shape using `TubeGeometry` + `CatmullRomCurve3` (brown wood-like) |
