## What's in the demo

| Part | Geometry | Details |
|---|---|---|
| **Fabric wrap** | Open `CylinderGeometry` + circle caps | Canvas-generated woven crosshatch texture, beige color |
| **Central pad** | `RoundedBoxGeometry` + partial sphere dome | Soft white with subtle noise texture, sits raised on top of the wrap |
| **Adhesive tabs** | `ExtrudeGeometry` from custom shape | Curved flaps at each end, tan color |
| **Lighting** | Ambient + directional key/fill + rim point light | ACES filmic tone mapping, soft PCF shadows |
| **Animation** | Gentle sine-wave float + slow Y-rotation | Makes the bandage feel alive |
| **Interaction** | `OrbitControls` with damping | Drag to orbit, scroll to zoom |

