This creates a **full 3D character head with a detailed beard** featuring:

- **Head** — warm-toned sphere with subtle proportions
- **Face details** — eyes with whites/pupils, eyebrows, nose, mouth, ears
- **Beard** built from **~270 individual hair strands** using `TubeGeometry` along `CatmullRomCurve3` curves, covering:
  - Main chin beard (80 strands, longest)
  - Mustache (40 strands)
  - Left & right sideburns (60 strands)
  - Left & right cheek fills (70 strands)
  - 15 extra long wispy accent hairs
- **Varied hair colors** in warm browns for realism
- **Three-point lighting** (ambient, directional, rim) with shadows
- **Gentle animation** — the head/beard slowly sways side-to-side with subtle hair wiggle
- **Floating sparkle particles** for atmosphere
- **Responsive** to window resizing

