**What's included:**

| Part | Geometry | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Body** | `CylinderGeometry` (open-ended) | Main cup walls, double-sided so you can see inside |
| **Bottom** | Thin `CylinderGeometry` | Solid base |
| **Rim** | `TorusGeometry` | Flared outer lip |
| **Inner rim** | Smaller `TorusGeometry` | Visible inner edge |
| **Handle** | Partial `TorusGeometry` (π×1.4 arc) | C-shaped handle attached to the side |

