## What's Included

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Helmet Parts** | Dome, brow ridge, face plate, cross-slit eye opening, nose guard, breathing holes, side cheek guards, neck guard, leather lining, decorative rivets |
| **Materials** | PBR metallic steel (main), dark metal (rivets/crest), brown leather (lining), dark inner (eye/breath holes) |
| **Lighting** | 5-point setup — ambient, key, fill, rim, and bottom fill for dramatic metallic reflections |
| **Animation** | Gentle auto-rotation + floating bob |
| **Controls** | OrbitControls — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom |
| **Environment** | Dark pedestal, ground plane, fog, ACES filmic tone mapping |

Just save as `index.html` and open in any modern browser — no build step needed.

