## What you get

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Mask geometry** | A stylised Venetian-style mask built from spheres, a nose bridge, gold-rimmed eye holes, cheek lines, a diamond forehead emblem, chin guard, and leather straps |
| **Materials** | Red face plate, dark strap interior, metallic gold accents with subtle emissive glow |
| **Lighting** | Three-point setup — warm key, blue rim, orange bottom fill — plus ambient |
| **Animation** | The mask gently floats and sways; a golden ground ring pulses |
| **Particles** | 600 warm floating dust motes for atmosphere |
| **Interaction** | OrbitControls — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom, with damping |

