## What you get

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Mitten body** | Deformed sphere — squashed palm, elongated finger compartment, rounded tip |
| **Thumb** | Cylinder + sphere, rotated outward on the side |
| **Cuff** | Open cylinder with top/bottom torus rims and 5 horizontal knit-rib rings |
| **Seams** | Tube geometry tracing the top center line and thumb division |
| **Decoration** | White hexagonal patch with a red 5-point star on the finger side |
| **Materials** | Warm red `MeshStandardMaterial` with high roughness for a fabric feel |
| **Lighting** | Key (warm), fill (cool blue), rim (orange point), ambient — all casting soft shadows |
| **Animation** | Gentle floating bob + slow sway |
| **Interaction** | `OrbitControls` — drag to orbit, scroll to zoom |

