## What you get

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Body** | Oblate sphere with vertex displacement creating stem & blossom dimples |
| **Skin texture** | Procedural noise bumps + a generated normal map for that pitted citrus look |
| **Stem** | Small brown cylinder at the north pole |
| **Leaf** | Curved green leaf attached to the stem |
| **Lighting** | 3-point setup (key, fill, rim) + ambient, ACES filmic tone mapping |
| **Ground** | Reflective metallic disc beneath for subtle reflections |
| **Animation** | Gentle idle rotation + floating bob |
| **Interaction** | Orbit controls — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom |

