## What's in the scene

| Element | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Main pipe** | `TubeGeometry` along a CatmullRom spline — runs horizontal, bends up, then horizontal again |
| **Branch pipe** | Secondary `TubeGeometry` splitting off via a **tee joint** (sphere) |
| **Flanges** | Positioned at 3 points along the main curve, each with **6 bolts** |
| **End caps** | Capped at all open pipe ends |
| **Materials** | High-metalness `MeshStandardMaterial` for realistic steel look |
| **Lighting** | Directional + two colored point lights with subtle pulsing animation |
| **Ground** | Dark plane with a grid helper, shadow receiving |
| **Controls** | `OrbitControls` with damping — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom |

