| **Physics** | Verlet integration with distance constraints across 80 segments |
| **Wind** | Sinusoidal breeze that increases toward the free end |
| **Interaction** | Click & drag any point on the rope to pull it around |
| **Visuals** | Tube geometry along a CatmullRom spline, ACES tone mapping, fog, shadows |
| **Camera** | OrbitControls — drag empty space to orbit, scroll to zoom |
| **Details** | Metallic anchor sphere at top, torus hook at bottom, grid floor for depth |

