## What's in this demo

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Shield body** | A classic heater-shield shape built with `THREE.Shape` + cubic Bézier curves, extruded with bevel for thickness |
| **Gold rim** | A ring created by subtracting an inner hole shape from an outer shield outline |
| **Cross emblem** | Two intersecting `BoxGeometry` bars in gold centered on the shield face |
| **Materials** | `MeshStandardMaterial` with high metalness/low roughness for a polished metallic look (red body, gold trim) |
| **Lighting** | Ambient + directional (warm key light) + blue rim light + orange point light for dramatic shading |
| **Camera** | `OrbitControls` with damping — drag to orbit, scroll to zoom |
| **Animation** | Gentle auto-rotation on the Y axis |

