## What you get

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **The Void** | A central black sphere with a pulsing blue-violet Fresnel rim glow (custom shader) |
| **Particles** | 12,000 points spawned in a wide sphere, drawn inward by an inverse-square pull + tangential vortex force |
| **Recycling** | Particles that reach the center are respawned at the outer edge with fresh random positions & colors |
| **Camera** | Slowly orbits the void so you can see the spiral from all angles |
| **Additive blending** | Gives the particle streams a glowing, ethereal look as they converge |

