## What's Inside

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Open head (C-shape)** | Two jaws + crossbar + inner gripping faces + back lip |
| **Closed head (box end)** | Hexagonal socket with dark inner hole |
| **Handle** | Cylinder with 12 grip ridges (torus segments) and end cap |
| **Materials** | Metallic `MeshStandardMaterial` with high metalness, low roughness for a chrome-steel look |
| **Lighting** | Directional key light + blue fill + warm rim point light + ambient |
| **Shadows** | `PCFSoftShadowMap` cast onto a dark ground plane |
| **Animation** | Gentle sine-wave float and tilt |
| **Controls** | `OrbitControls` — drag to rotate, scroll to zoom |

